Commercial Use Inquiry Process:
For commercial use inquiries, please contact: email@narenkram.com

To initiate a commercial use request:
1. Provide a detailed description of your intended use of the Software.
2. Outline your proposed business model and how the Software will be incorporated.
3. Suggest initial terms for profit sharing or compensation.

The copyright holder will review each request and respond within 30 business days.
Approved commercial use will require a separate written agreement.